# AI-Powered System Monitoring & Analysis Platform
## Requirements & Technical Specification Document

**Version:** 1.0  
**Date:** February 6, 2026  
**Status:** Draft  
**Document Type:** Technical Requirements & Specification

---

## Document Information

**Purpose:** This document defines the requirements, specifications, and design for an intelligent system monitoring and analysis platform that combines observability data from New Relic with source code context from GitHub, analyzed by AI to provide actionable insights and automated recommendations.

**Audience:** Engineering teams, product managers, architects, and stakeholders involved in development and operations.

