## 4. Data Flow

### 4.1 Analysis Workflow

```
1. TRIGGER
   ├─ Scheduled (cron)
   ├─ On-demand (CLI/API)
   ├─ Event-driven (New Relic alert)
   └─ Continuous (daemon mode)

2. DATA COLLECTION
   ├─ New Relic MCP Client
   │  ├─ Fetch metrics (last 24h)
   │  ├─ Fetch errors (last 24h)
   │  ├─ Fetch traces (sample)
   │  └─ Fetch infrastructure metrics
   │
   └─ GitHub MCP Client
      ├─ Fetch recent commits (last 7 days)
      ├─ Get current codebase snapshot
      └─ Fetch relevant files based on errors

3. DATA NORMALIZATION
   ├─ Convert to unified format
   ├─ Build temporal context
   └─ Create ContextDocument

4. AI ANALYSIS (Multi-stage)
   
   Stage 1: Quick Health Check
   ├─ Calculate health score
   ├─ Identify critical issues
   └─ Determine if deep dive needed
   
   Stage 2: Issue Analysis (for each issue)
   ├─ Root cause analysis
   ├─ Impact assessment
   └─ Priority ranking
   
   Stage 3: Solution Generation
   ├─ Code fixes
   ├─ Configuration changes
   └─ Best practices
   
   Stage 4: Validation
   ├─ Verify recommendations feasibility
   └─ Check for conflicts

5. REPORT GENERATION
   ├─ Format results
   ├─ Add visualizations
   └─ Include actionable steps

6. NOTIFICATION
   ├─ Alert if critical
   ├─ Send report
   └─ Update dashboard

7. STORAGE (for learning)
   ├─ Store analysis results
   ├─ Track recommendation outcomes
   └─ Build historical database
```

### 4.2 Data Collection Sequence Diagram

```
User/Scheduler        DataCollector    NR_MCP_Client    GH_MCP_Client    AI_Engine
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |--analyze_app-------->|                 |                |              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--get_metrics--->|                |              |
     |                      |<--metrics-------|                |              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--get_errors---->|                |              |
     |                      |<--errors--------|                |              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--get_traces---->|                |              |
     |                      |<--traces--------|                |              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--get_recent_commits------------->|              |
     |                      |<--commits-----------------------|              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--get_code_for_errors------------>|              |
     |                      |<--code---------------------------|              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--normalize_data()                               |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |--analyze_context---------------------------->|
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |                 |                |  [AI Processing]
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |                      |<--analysis_result---------------------------|
     |                      |                 |                |              |
     |<--report-------------|                 |                |              |
     |                      |                 |                |              |
```

