## 5. MCP Integrations

### 5.1 Model Context Protocol (MCP) Overview

MCP là protocol chuẩn để AI models có thể interact với external data sources một cách an toàn và có cấu trúc.

**Key Concepts:**
- **Resources**: Named data entities (files, API endpoints)
- **Tools**: Functions AI có thể call
- **Prompts**: Reusable prompt templates
- **Sampling**: Request AI model completions

### 5.2 New Relic MCP Integration

**MCP Server Configuration:**
```python
# New Relic MCP Server exposes these tools

TOOLS = [
    {
        "name": "get_apm_metrics",
        "description": "Fetch APM metrics for an application",
        "parameters": {
            "app_id": "string",
            "metric_names": "array<string>",
            "time_range": "object"
        }
    },
    {
        "name": "query_nrql",
        "description": "Execute NRQL query",
        "parameters": {
            "query": "string",
            "account_id": "string"
        }
    },
    {
        "name": "get_error_traces",
        "description": "Get error traces with stack traces",
        "parameters": {
            "app_id": "string",
            "error_class": "optional<string>",
            "limit": "optional<int>"
        }
    }
]

RESOURCES = [
    {
        "uri": "newrelic://app/{app_id}/metrics",
        "name": "Application Metrics",
        "description": "Real-time metrics for application"
    },
    {
        "uri": "newrelic://app/{app_id}/errors",
        "name": "Application Errors",
        "description": "Error traces and exceptions"
    }
]
```

**Usage Example:**
```python
# AI model can call these tools through MCP
result = mcp_client.call_tool(
    "get_apm_metrics",
    {
        "app_id": "12345",
        "metric_names": ["HttpDispatcher", "Apdex", "Errors/all"],
        "time_range": {"since": "1 hour ago"}
    }
)
```

