### 12.2 Business Impact Metrics

| Metric | Target | Measurement |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| **MTTR reduction** | -50% | Mean time to resolution |
| **Proactive detection** | > 70% | Issues found before user reports |
| **Cost savings** | $500+/month | Infrastructure optimization impact |
| **Developer time saved** | 10+ hrs/week | Time spent on manual monitoring |

### 12.3 AI Quality Metrics

```python
@dataclass
class RecommendationOutcome:
    recommendation_id: str
    issue_type: str
    ai_suggestion: str
    was_implemented: bool
    was_effective: bool  # Did it fix the issue?
    developer_feedback: str
    confidence_score: float
    
# Track over time to improve prompts
def calculate_ai_accuracy(outcomes: List[RecommendationOutcome]) -> float:
    effective = [o for o in outcomes if o.was_implemented and o.was_effective]
    implemented = [o for o in outcomes if o.was_implemented]
    return len(effective) / len(implemented) if implemented else 0.0
```

